snippet.title: Titanfall: IMC Rising Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the latest map pack Titanfall: IMC Rising.
Battle your way through Backwater, Zone 18, and Sand Trap as you continue the fight for the frontier.
More information on Titanfall and the latest expansions here: http://titanfall.com/dlc
